    <sym>Campground</sym>
    <extensions>
      <scenery>6</scenery>
    </extensions>
  </wpt>
  <wpt lat="38.22608" lon="-107.38515">
    <name>ALPINE RANGER STATION</name>
    <desc>Overview The Alpine Ranger Station is situated on the Alpine Plateau at 9,600 feet, in a beautiful alpine valley surrounded by aspen, spruce and fir forest. With inspiring views and multiple nearby recreation opportunities, the Ranger Station is just the place for a quiet and historic retreat, with a few modern amenities. Recreation Surrounded by miles of National Forest, visitors to the Alpine Ranger Station can enjoy a multitude of outdoor activities. There are several hiking and mountain biki...</desc>
