  <wpt lat="45.6238889" lon="-114.3019444">
    <name>ALTA CAMPGROUND</name>
    <desc>Overview Alta Campground is located in a scenic forest in the heart of Montana&apos;s Bitterroot National Forest. The West Fork of the Bitterroot River flows nearby, giving visitors access to some of the best fishing the area has to offer, as well as other water-related recreation. Recreation Fly fishing and wading in the Bitterroot River, which runs alongside the campground, are popular activities. A variety of trails and unimproved roads are great for exploring by bike or off-road vehicle. Hiking t...</desc>
