  <wpt lat="45.1162889" lon="-113.45795">
    <name>BLOODY DICK CABIN</name>
    <desc>Overview Bloody Dick Cabin, named after the English Trapper Richard &quot;Bloody&quot; Leigh, is a small wood frame cabin. Nestled in the evergreens near Reservoir Lake in Southwestern Montana&apos;s Bitterroot Mountains - the cabin is available for rental year-round. Popularity peaks during the summer and fall seasons with hikers, ohv enthusiasts, and big game hunters. During spring and winter, the nearby lake freezes promoting ice fishing while several area winter trails offer cross-country skiing and snowmo...</desc>
    <type>Campground</type>
    <sym>Campground</sym>
    <extensions>
