    <name>Bridalveil Creek Campground</name>
    <desc>Overview Bridalveil Creek Campground is closed for the 2025 season. Staying at Bridalveil Creek Campground requires reservations. There are no first come, first served sites available. Bridalveil Creek is located in breathtaking Yosemite National Park in Central California&apos;s rugged Sierra Nevada Mountain Range. The site is situated on Glacier Point Road at an elevation of 7,200 feet, 26 miles from Yosemite Valley. Within Yosemite, visitors can gaze upon waterfalls, sheer granite cliffs, deep val...</desc>
