    <name>Buttercup Ranger Station</name>
    <desc>Buttercup Ranger Station is located off of Grey&apos;s Well Road near Interstate 8. This station offers visitors a location to purchase their dunes permit, gather information and seek medical aid. This station is open Friday through Sunday from mid-October to mid-April during the high visitation period.</desc>
