  </wpt>
  <wpt lat="34.2611111" lon="-93.1875">
    <name>CADDO DRIVE</name>
    <desc>Overview Caddo Drive Campground sits along the pristine shores of Degray Lake in the foothills of the Quachita Mountains. The area offers stunning scenery and panoramic views, and Caddo was awarded one of Americas Top 25 Scenic Views. Recreation DeGray Lake hosts thousands of professional fishing tournaments, triathlons and it is one of the most popular swimming destinations in the region. The area is also ideal for boating and jet skiing. Facilities Caddo Drive offers a mix of RV, standard and ...</desc>
