    <name>Chimney Rock Campground</name>
    <desc>Along the Chimney Rock segment of Central Oregon&apos;s Crooked Wild and Scenic River, Chimney Rock campground offers a relaxing woodland setting amongst Western Juniper trees and beneath massive Columbia River rock formations. Fly-fishing and hiking on the nearby Chimney Rock trail offer day-long recreational fun. Enjoy plenty of easy river access along the adjacent Crooked River Back Country Byway, State Highway 27. Know Before You Go: Chimney Rock Campground is open year-round and is equipped with...</desc>
