    <desc>This sweet destination of a campground rests a short distance from the 1.34 million acre Selway-Bitterroot Wilderness. Located just 24 miles south of Highway 12, you&apos;ll have available to you 15 campsites, stock facilities, stunning scenery, and access to some of the nation&apos;s wildest country including many remote alpine lakes and mountain peaks. Hoodoo Lake is just a short stroll from the campground.</desc>
