  </wpt>
  <wpt lat="43.7725361" lon="-121.6203056">
    <name>FALL RIVER CAMPGROUND</name>
    <desc>Overview Fall River Campground is located along Fall River within the Deschutes National Forest west of La Pine. Recreation Campers can enjoy the nearby Fall River Trail which offers frequent views of crystal clear Fall River. This trail can be accessed from one of three Fall River Trailheads . Visitors can also enjoy fishing on Fall River although it is limited to fly fishing only. Facilities Fall River Campground sites tend to be on the smaller side without any RV hookups or services. Campers ...</desc>
