    <desc>Overview Halfway Flat Campground is located about 30 miles west of Naches, Washington on the east side of the Cascades mountain range. Recreation The campground setting provides ready access to the Naches River, where fishing is popular. Hiking and horseback riding trails extend into the William O. Douglas and Norse Peak Wilderness areas, and off-road vehicle and snowmobile access draws visitors to the Little Naches drainage. Halfway Flat Campground is conveniently located 30 minutes below the s...</desc>
