    <name>Historic Bushman House (Gettysburg)</name>
    <desc>Overview The historic Bushman House is an exceptional year-round place to stay and is located within the Gettysburg National Military Park, where it witnessed the Battle of Gettysburg. Beautifully restored and updated in 2017, the house is set back from the roadways and nestled within famous landmarks like Little Round Top and Devil&apos;s Den, and near the historic town of Gettysburg. Recreation There are numerous ways to experience the battlefield. Visit the park&apos;s Things to Do page to learn about ...</desc>
