    <name>Joe Elliot Yellow Post Sites</name>
    <desc>These two remote yellow post sites are located near the end of Forest Road 1N34 (San Sevaine Road) accessible from Lytle Creek Road. This narrow steep dirt road is open only to high clearance vehicles and four wheel-drive may also be required. This road is also only open during certain months of the year and is subject to closures due to Red Flag warnings or winter storms. The seasonal closure of Road 1N34 begins on March 1 and extends through Labor Day each year to protect important fawning hab...</desc>
