  </wpt>
  <wpt lat="56.5302778" lon="-133.1419444">
    <name>KAH SHEETS BAY CABIN</name>
    <desc>Overview Kah Sheets Bay Cabin sits on coastal waters in the islands of southeastern Alaska. It is remotely located, offering solace and seclusion to visitors, but also access to great fishing, hunting and wildlife viewing. The cabin is accessible by boat or float plane, or may be reached by hiking the 2.75-mile trail from Kah Sheets Lake, which is accessible by float plane only. Visitors are responsible for their own travel arrangements and safety, and must bring several of their own amenities. ...</desc>
    <type>Campground</type>
