    <desc>Overview Maple Canyon Campground is known for its unique cliffs, arches, and scenic views of the Sanpitch Mountains. It is a small campground nestled between towering conglomerate rock walls on either side of the canyon. A favorite among rock climbers, notably for a formation called The Pipe Dream, the campground is just 3 miles from Freedom, Utah. Recreation Rock climbing is the campground&apos;s main draw, attracting climbers from all over the world with its numerous routes for beginners and expert...</desc>
