  <wpt lat="40.9286111" lon="-109.7241667">
    <name>NAVAJO CLIFFS</name>
    <desc>Overview Navajo Cliffs is an ideal group day-use site for weddings, reunions and large gatherings. It&apos;s just 7 miles south of Manila, Utah, along the scenic Sheep Creek Geological Loop at an elevation of 6,200 feet. Recreation Sheep Creek offers rainbow trout and kokanee salmon fishing. Boating, fishing, canoeing, water skiing and swimming are popular activities on nearby Flaming Gorge. Facilities This group day-use site can accommodate up to 80 people. Large picnic tables, a serving table, gril...</desc>
