    <desc>Overview North Campground is located in the beautiful and unique Bryce Canyon National Park. Known for its colorful rock spires and grand vistas that sweep out over the High Plateaus region of the Colorado Plateau, Bryce Canyon is the ultimate camping destination. Located at an approximate elevation of 8,000 feet (2438 m), the campground is centrally located within walking distance of the park&apos;s Visitor Center. Famed Sunrise and Sunset Points are located nearby, at the heart of the magnificent g...</desc>
