    <name>OAK BOTTOM CAMPGROUND</name>
    <desc>Overview PLEASE NOTE THIS IS NOT OAK BOTTOM CAMPGROUND AT WHISKEYTOWN LAKE. FOR THAT SITE NEAR REDDING, CALL 530-359-2269 This Oak Bottom Campground is on the Salmon River at Somes Bar, CA situated on a gently sloping hillside in the expansive Six Rivers and Klamath National Forests. It offers a peaceful and shaded camping environment, far from highway noise and city distractions. NEW: Each reservable campsite now has its own bear-resistant food storage locker, as do most of the first-come first...</desc>
