  </wpt>
  <wpt lat="33.3416667" lon="-116.8786111">
    <name>OBSERVATORY CAMPGROUND</name>
    <desc>Overview Science buffs and families are drawn to Observatory Campground for its proximity to the Palomar Observatory, a world-class center of astronomy research operated by the California Institute of Technology. Just two miles from the observatory, the campground provides visitors with a unique learning experience in the great outdoors. The facility offers a variety of amenities for both tent and RV camping. Hiking, biking and picnicking can be found nearby. Recreation An exciting amateur astro...</desc>
    <type>Campground</type>
