    <name>Oak Fork Campground (Timothy Lake, OR)</name>
    <desc>Overview Oak Fork Campground is located on the shores of Timothy Lake in the shadow of Oregon&apos;s Mt. Hood. The surrounding forest setting offers spectacular views, miles of trails for exploration and abundant fishing. Recreation Proximity to Timothy Lake allows campers to enjoy a variety of water-related recreation activities, including boating and sailing, as well as swimming, windsurfing and fishing. Anglers can expect a catch of kokanee salmon and a variety of trout . A range of trails are loc...</desc>
