    <desc>Campsites with spectacular views of the Colorado River that accommodate tents only (no trailers or large vehicles). Individual sites are available on a first-come, first-serve basis. The campsites offer more secluded sites and beautiful views of the Colorado River canyon. (Do not enter the river without the required life jackets; it has dangerous under currents.) Individual Sites: 7 Fees: $20/night Water: No Toilets: Yes Hook-ups: No Individual Sites: 7 (limited to 10 people &amp; two vehicles per s...</desc>
