  <wpt lat="44.0491" lon="-120.377">
    <name>Ochoco NF-Maury Mountains Area</name>
    <desc>The Maury Mountains offer solitude and relaxation to those in search of it. There are four campgrounds in the area including one situated on the shore of Antelope Flat Reservoir (a little known fishing hole), and the agate beds near Elkhorn Campground have also been known to attract rock hounds. This beautiful, secluded area is a great place to find your own adventure!</desc>
