  <wpt lat="45.70742" lon="-115.54844">
    <name>Orogrande Campground #1 and #2</name>
    <desc>Locally known as Orogrande #1 and 2, this campground occupies both sides of the road, one on the bank of Crooked River. It includes a toilet, fire rings and at least three camp pads. The non-river side is a good spot for one family or small group. The river side is an open, grassy campsite.</desc>
