    <name>Pines Campground</name>
    <desc>The Pines Campground is on a mixed conifer forested site adjacent to the Little Golden Forest Trail and near the Groveland Ranger District Office. The campground includes a large group site. Each site has a picnic table and a campfire pit with a grill. Vault toilets and potable water is available in the campground during summer.</desc>
