    <name>RANCHERIA</name>
    <desc>Overview Rancheria Campground is located on the shores of Huntington Lake near the Kaiser Wilderness. The campsites sit under a dense canopy of fir and pine, and some tent-only sites are right on the shore and allow for informal mooring of boats. The campground&apos;s location makes it possible to discover all the activities and attractions at Huntington Lake, and it&apos;s an excellent base for further exploration of the Kaiser Wilderness. Recreation Many hiking trails are in the area, including Rancheri...</desc>
