    <name>Toto Creek Campground</name>
    <desc>Overview Toto Creek Campground lies approximately 30 miles north of Buford Dam on Lake Sidney Lanier. The site features beautiful views of the lake as well as excellent access to picnicking and boating. The lake, named for the poet, Sidney Lanier, is well known for its aqua-blue colored water, spectacular scenery and access to recreational activities. Each year, over 11 million people come to visit the lake. Recreation Toto Creek Campground offers many outdoor recreation opportunities including ...</desc>
