    <name>Transfer Park Campground</name>
    <desc>Transfer Park Campground is only 1 mile past Florida Campground, with 11 shaded acres above the Florida River. Two loops have 25 sites with shade and sun, and large, open play areas. The upper loop is mostly level, with several larger sites. The lower loop is near the river and has 2 larger sites, a few short pull-throughs, and several tent spots. Parking for the Burnt Timber Trail is near the campground. Services include water, trash pickup, fire grates, picnic tables, and pit toilets. Bear-saf...</desc>
