    <desc>Wolf Flats is a dispersed, undeveloped camping area with 25 locations to camp. Some large areas are can accommodate groups of 50 people. There is an adjacent undeveloped boat access to the South Fork of the Snake River. Fees/Rules/Facilities: • No fees • Pack out toilet and trash—No garbage collection at this facility • Do not burn metals, glass, or plastic in the fire pits. Wood products only. • Do not cut down trees • Only use dead and downed wood (only small diameter) • Do not create new camp...</desc>
