  <wpt lat="45.73632" lon="-110.259565">
    <name>Yellowstone District</name>
    <desc>The Yellowstone district includes a portion of the Crazy Mountains and covers the northeast section of the Custer Gallatin National Forest south of Big Timber and east of the Yellowstone river. It also includes an area of land to the west of the Yellowstone river adjacent to the east side of the Bozeman district.</desc>
